data.description: SELLER IS OFFERING $3000 TOWARDS BUYERS CLOSING COST! Stunning 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home nestled in a cul-de-sac, in the desired Meadow Glen subdivision. Immaculate and meticulously cared for, this fantastic open floor plan has the primary bedroom downstairs with a spacious bathroom, garden tub, separate shower and walk in closet. Gourmet kitchen with granite counter tops, large island and gas cooktop, plenty of cabinets and counter space. Office at the front of the home, over looks the front yard, perfect for working from home. Upstairs features game room with built in work station and covered balcony, 3 additional bedrooms and a media room. Media projector, screen, and security cameras covey with the home. Backyard oasis awaits you, large backyard with covered patio and a HOT TUB...prefect for entertaining!! Community offers playground and pool, just around the corner. This beauty will not last long!
